add_teach_offer -  This method adds a teaching offer to the living object.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void add_teach_offer(object ob,
string skill,
int num,
int lvl,
int xp)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^ob%^RESET%^ - the object teaching us
%^BOLD%^skill%^RESET%^ - the skill they are teaching
%^BOLD%^num%^RESET%^ - the number of levels they are teaching
%^BOLD%^lvl%^RESET%^ - the level they are teaching us from
%^BOLD%^xp%^RESET%^ - the cost of the level increase in xp

